<p>But let's focus on the positive, 96.61% means you have a chance to win! Plus, it's way more likely to hit the jackpot in this game than crossing Park Place with a hotel on it on the board game Monopoly. So, the math might not be taken too seriously, but at least it indicates that Monopoly: Utility Trails is a fairly balanced online slot game that could bring you luck and entertainment for some time.</p>"
}

